weirdness of quantum physics.

00:01:40.910 --> 00:01:43.550 align:middle line:10%
And I realized that
there's no good explanation

00:01:43.550 --> 00:01:45.350 align:middle line:10%
for some of that weirdness.

00:01:45.350 --> 00:01:47.510 align:middle line:10%
But it turns out
within video games,

00:01:47.510 --> 00:01:49.850 align:middle line:10%
